modName: Become the new jarl of whiterun
summary:
BECOME THE JARL OF WHITERUN!
command your soldiers and your court mage!
descriptionHtml:
this is just a savegame in which i have \"disposed\" of the original guards and the jarl in dragonsreach and replaced them with stormcloak soldier companions that will obey your commands. 

this is solely for roleplay purposes only, it will prevent you from completing any quests relating to the jarl of whiterun.

to install go to c:\\users\\<your name>\\my documents\\my games\\skyrim\\saves then paste the save file in there.

HAVE FUN! =D
author: dod667
